{"tid":1956021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共 : 武漢肺炎疫苗展開首階段臨床試驗 108名志願者接種 有人曾低燒頭痛","createTime":"2020-04-03T01:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T02:42:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4da69d5e8089feaca5fe19f4765b60a9b81491","tid":1956021,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"武漢108人接種新冠疫苗 有人曾低燒頭痛<br />\n03.04.2020 07:56<br />\n內地上月啟動新型冠狀病毒疫病首階段臨床試驗，內地傳媒報導，湖北武漢至今有108名志願者接種新型冠狀病毒疫苗，當中18人完成隔離，全部人在解除隔離時身體狀況良好。報導引述一名接受過低劑量疫苗並完成隔離的志願者表示，接種疫苗後曾經低燒及頭痛，但症狀很快消退，在14日隔離期間，每一日都要測體溫和做健康記錄。<br />\n<br />\n研究團隊未來會繼續跟進志願者狀況，為他們體檢，為期半年，團隊叮囑志願者要注意身體，不要感染其他傳染病，以免影響疫苗效果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278458&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278458%26csid%3D261_341&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BrHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=d568b4eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278458&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9f7fcc7dc139f61490772c56dc2c00b83ce7fcf4","tid":1956021,"uid":51933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"團隊叮囑志願者要注意身體，不要感染其他傳染病，以免影響疫苗效果。<br />\n<br />\n成個頭盔粒定先<br />\n你死撚左一定係你錯"},{"pid":"448790d7be355a03fc01a3d3ac41604d3faf32a9","tid":1956021,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0b1664a7f9a8d68ba6d3edabb3ecee7de92a9e","tid":1956021,"uid":278261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"有20% 成功都可以楊名立萬， 光宗耀祖， 為國爭光架"},{"pid":"371ee3a8f102723373079e4342619b5b9ea6e110","tid":1956021,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"黑心疫苗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /